the soul may yet scream on.

It shuns fear.

And the skill of compulsion."

When to swing like crazy, and when to run.

name: Daresso's Courage
explicitMods: 36% Chance to Block Spell Damage while on Low Life
flavourText: By tourney's end, Daresso bled and shivered.
Yet even accursed treachery failed to steal the champion's victory.

explicitMods: +3 Life gained for each Enemy hit by Attacks

that the intelligent spirit in this sword
does not like to share its master's attention

name: Shiversting

and all but the strong and the stupid
seek shelter from their grasp until daybreak.

name: Ungil's Gauche
explicitMods: +12% Chance to Block Attack Damage while Dual Wielding
flavourText: Unwieldy and garish became graceful
and deadly in Ungil's nimble hands.

name: Saffell's Frame
flavourText: A swift mind solves problems before they occur.

name: Geofri's Baptism
flavourText: "One quick tap is all the persuasion you'll need."
- Archbishop Geofri of Phrecia Cathedral

Applies Level 15 Elemental Weakness on Blocking a Spell, ignoring Curse Limit

Open your mind and you will see the cracks in your enemy's plans.

name: Lioneye's Paws
explicitMods: Adds 12 to 24 Fire Damage to Attacks
40% reduced Movement Speed when on Low Life
Cannot be Stunned when on Low Life
flavourText: Stand and lead the righteous pride,
Fight till death, never hide.

explicitMods: 0.6% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Life
0.4% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Mana
flavourText: A soft caress in dead of night,
that slips about the neck, so tight.

name: Ashrend
explicitMods: 10% increased Physical Damage with Ranged Weapons

explicitMods: 1% increased Movement Speed per Frenzy Charge
Regenerate 15 Life per second per Endurance Charge
100% increased Endurance, Frenzy and Power Charge Duration
flavourText: Use the dead to stave off death,
An armour of bones and rot.
Hanging on with bated breath,
One lapse and all for naught.

name: Bated Breath
flavourText: At knifepoint, a moment's hesitation means death.

name: Dreadarc
explicitMods: Curse Enemies with Flammability on Hit
flavourText: The fastest way to a man's heart
is through his sternum.

name: Perandus Blazon
explicitMods: -2 Physical Damage taken from Attack Hits

into an enemy, and the Perandus family
had more debtors than anyone.

Carry wisdom for the living,
If you are willing to give your life
To listen.

Corruption, perversion, sin?
No. It is progress.
You simply lack the means to see it."
- Inquisitor Maligaro

name: Kingsguard

name: Solaris Lorica
explicitMods: Chaos Damage does not bypass Energy Shield

They are for the weak and frightened.
Instead, light the path to greatness,
So that I may begin my bright pursuit.

explicitMods: +100 to Evasion Rating while on Low Life

Spirit comes to take you on your final journey.

Leaders are born in ruins and flames.

- Hyrri of the Karui

the flame inside still blazed bright after her death,
and so did hers.

name: Eclipse Solaris
explicitMods: 133% increased Critical Strike Chance against Blinded Enemies

Each time, Solaris emerges from Lunaris, born anew.

name: Blackgleam
implicitMods: Adds 2 to 4 Fire Damage to Attacks

name: Death's Harp
explicitMods: Bow Attacks fire an additional Arrow
flavourText: The mournful music of the strings,
The creaking arch, the arrow sings.
A choking cry, a rattled breath,
The Reaper's Song, the Harp of Death.

name: Infractem
flavourText: Mark us with mercy, then press on with care,
Execute us steadily, notch away at our despair.

name: Relentless Fury

Sunder my every foe
Fuel my boiling blood

she forged a new destiny.
Sacrificing the ephemeral joys of man,
she embraced the eternal grasp of nature.
Seizing her one true wish,
she found peace at last.

Your hate is our infinity
The fire rises!

name: Voidhome

Though countless corpses lie in wake.

To the tallest redwoods,
Life endures in Wraeclast.

Licks the skin and flesh from the fearful

There is no flame

To crush the very light of day.

Fear is the wound left untended.

And your opponent is bleeding you dry,
There is only one appropriate response:
Unbridled, overwhelming violence."
- Daresso, the Sword King

Than the Belly of the Beast

30% chance to Trigger a Socketed Lightning Spell on Hit

name: Deidbell

name: The Ignomon

An anomaly defying all odds
The "unkillable" beast met the divine
And Ventor met his latest trophy.

name: Atziri's Mirror

As the lightning stilled his heart,
But it was the flames upon his lover's face
That roused him to vengeance."
- From 'The Three Dragons' by Victario of Sarn

name: Greed's Embrace

The rest were already dead.

name: Rumi's Concoction

+13% Chance to Block Spell Damage during Flask effect

Today I am wise, so I am changing myself."
-Rumi of the Vaal

name: Geofri's Crest

Not so, the battle for survival.

name: Chober Chaber

+1 to Level of Socketed Minion Gems

name: Ornament of the East

choke the rain in the very clouds.
Both life and land feel the thirst.

Only victory.

Voll proved disastrous in times of peace.

And trapped for a thousand years,
The lonely moon weeps

name: Lioneye's Glare

He burned as a torch in the blackest night
She shone as ice in the winter sun
Proudly, fiercely
At their mother's side, forever.

will burn in the minds of men forever.

name: Asenath's Mark

as the fingers that drew her bowstring.

name: Lochtonial Caress
flavourText: Why cling to your sanity? It offers you nothing.
Surrender to me, and I will grant you everything.

name: Ezomyte Peak
flavourText: Centuries of servitude, a day
of glory, an eternity of death.

name: Malachai's Simula
flavourText: It was a sliver of Malachai's soul
that animated the first Eternal Guardian.

at an Eternal Champion in steel and gold,
The first to challenge its treacherous traps.
To mark the occasion, Izaro had the Champion's remains gilded.

with flames and ice.

- Archbishop Geofri

name: Dusktoe

the petty frictions of one's life."
- Inquisitor Maligaro

flavourText: The eagle knows nothing
but the scream and the strike.

name: Marohi Erqi

It mattered little. When Erqi's maul fell true, so did its target.

name: Cloak of Defiance

As eyes weep,
When the hand grips hard
With trembling fingers,
When belly twists
Yet legs stand strong,
That is the work
Of the Defiant Heart.

name: Stone of Lazhwar
flavourText: You are slow, foolish and ignorant.
I am not.

name: The Searing Touch
implicitMods: +12% Chance to Block Attack Damage while wielding a Staff
explicitMods: +2 to Level of all Fire Spell Skill Gems
flavourText: Burn to cinders, scar and maim,
Rule a world, bathed in flame.

name: Icetomb

At the end of time,
the world will perish in ice.

name: Wurm's Molt
explicitMods: 0.4% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Life
0.4% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Mana

in every skin the great beasts shed.

name: Goldrim

name: Heatshiver
explicitMods: +1 to Level of Socketed Fire Gems
+1 to Level of Socketed Cold Gems
flavourText: Give of your heated passions.
Give of your cold resolve.
You will be repaid.

name: Gang's Momentum
flavourText: Become one with the unstoppable flame.

name: Hyaon's Fury
explicitMods: 3% increased Damage taken per Frenzy Charge
12% increased Lightning Damage per Frenzy Charge
+20 Life gained on Kill per Frenzy Charge
flavourText: "Hyaon the 'Red Wolf'
Howling mad
Cloaked in blood
A banner to his legion
A terror to his foes."
- Garivaldi, Chronicler to the Empire

name: Doomsower
explicitMods: Socketed Melee Gems have 15% increased Area of Effect
Socketed Red Gems get 10% Physical Damage as Extra Fire Damage
flavourText: So the seed of hate was born,
Evil forged and Hope forsworn.

name: Storm Cloud
flavourText: Centuries of development in steel armoursmithing
turned the armies of the Eternal Empire
into very effective lightning rods.

name: Pillar of the Caged God
implicitMods: +12% Chance to Block Attack Damage while wielding a Staff
explicitMods: 1% increased Area of Effect per 20 Intelligence
16% increased Physical Weapon Damage per 10 Strength

Destined to serve the monkey's paw
Strong as a tower of iron
Deft as the needle doubt

A scar of the mind you'll never remember.

name: Taryn's Shiver

A scaly frost-encrusted thorn.
All who feel its wintry light
Shiver in pain at the frozen dawn.

name: Rime Gaze
explicitMods: Socketed Gems are Supported by Level 15 Concentrated Effect
flavourText: The malice in her gaze froze blood and shattered bone.

name: Timeclasp
explicitMods: Temporal Chains has 30% reduced Effect on you

I'm just evening things out."
- Doryani, Queen's Thaumaturgist

name: Rise of the Phoenix

100% increased Accuracy Rating when on Low Life

name: Goldwyrm

name: Carnage Heart

its thirst has only begun.

name: Apep's Rage

name: Lightbane Raiment

Zahndethus cast aside his faith
and embraced the darkness.

name: Queen's Decree

She let the peasants take their wealth.
The peasants wanted to take her wealth.
She let the soldiers take their heads.
The soldiers wanted to take her head.
She sat on her throne and wept.

name: Kaltenhalt
explicitMods: Reflects 48 Cold Damage to Melee Attackers

name: Sidhebreath
explicitMods: 0.2% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Mana

name: Doedre's Damning

there was only a whirling, black void.

name: Crest of Perandus

name: Springleaf

name: Bramblejack

-2 Physical Damage taken from Attack Hits

name: Wideswing

of seven men in a single cleave.

name: Lori's Lantern
